						               													<description>Hawksworld is a 2 to 4 player strategic board game where opponents fight for resources and strategic objectives in order to achieve VICTORY.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Inspired by the best Real Time Strategy computer games, Hawksworld successfully translates into a turn based board game the escalation, tactical nuances, and delicate balancing between claiming resources, upgrading tech, and maintaining supremacy on the battleground.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;While players build their armies on the battlefield they also use engine building mechanics, worker placement and a programmable system for issuing orders that creates a pace and escalation culminating in some murderously tense moments right up until the final moves of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Exploring the map and revealing terrain and resources sets the tone in the early game.&amp;#10;Capturing resources, building a base and a force to match the challenges before you shapes the mid game.&amp;#10;Finally, each factions force fights to claim strategic objectives to win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
